{
  "texts": [
    "Accuracy values of 89% is achieved for predicting AD conversion in a 54 MCI sample subjects and 87% are obtained in 87 sample subjects, that includes 33 HCs.",
    "The proposed Deep-MEG technique is useful for early detection of changes in the spectral-temporal connectivity profiles.",
    "However, the results of three-class classification (HC, pMCI, sMCI) are not satisfactory.",
    "Also, Balboni et al. (2022) used spatial warping network segmentation to segment the MRI scans.",
    "The implementation is performed using Python 3.6.9 along with the Keras and TensorFlow libraries."
  ]
}